{"id":2991,"date":"2025-06-05T13:38:05","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:38:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2991"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:19:28","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:19:28","slug":"da-mong-lo-mao-mach-nen-dung-gi-chia-se-tu-chuyen-gia","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/da-mong-lo-mao-mach-nen-dung-gi-chia-se-tu-chuyen-gia\/","title":{"rendered":"Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? Chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch<\/strong> l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u0103n kho\u0103n c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, GSC s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea5t t\u1ea7n t\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mong-lo-mao-mach-la-sao\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 sao?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u nh\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1edbi da (th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf, t\u00edm ho\u1eb7c xanh) b\u1ecb gi\u00e3n n\u1edf v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i r\u00f5 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da m\u1ecfng nh\u01b0 hai b\u00ean m\u00e1, m\u0169i, v\u00f9ng th\u00e1i d\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf ch\u00e2n. C\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t li ti, \u0111an xen nh\u01b0 m\u1ea1ng nh\u1ec7n, g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3765\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3765\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3765\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-1.webp\" alt=\"Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 sao\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3765\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 sao<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0: n\u1ed5i g\u00e2n m\u00e1u, gi\u00e3n t\u0129nh m\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u1edbi da, hay suy gi\u00e3n m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-da-lai-bi-tinh-trang-da-mong-lo-mao-mach\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao da l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u01b0\u1edbi da gi\u00e3n n\u1edf v\u00e0 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lao-hoa-tu-nhien-cua-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e3o h\u00f3a t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Theo th\u1eddi gian, l\u00e0n da m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 collagen v\u00e0 elastin &#8211; hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a da. Khi c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec d\u1ea7n m\u1ecfng \u0111i, trong khi l\u1edbp m\u1ee1 d\u01b0\u1edbi da c\u0169ng co l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u1ed9 ra ngo\u00e0i, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tac-dong-tu-anh-nang-mat-troi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UV trong \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y l\u1edbp h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac collagen v\u00e0 elastin b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi. Khi da m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, c\u00e1c mao m\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u1edbi da s\u1ebd ph\u00ecnh to v\u00e0 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao nh\u1eefng ai th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ec5 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3766\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3766\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3766\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-2-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-2-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-2-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-2-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-2-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3766\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"yeu-to-di-truyen\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 di truy\u1ec1n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh ra \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da m\u1ecfng do di truy\u1ec1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed m\u1eafc c\u00e1c r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng Rothmund-Thomson, h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng Bloom hay tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 \u0111\u1ecf. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u1ec5 gi\u00e3n n\u1edf h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-quen-sinh-hoat-thieu-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c, u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia, hay thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u v\u00e0 tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, r\u01b0\u1ee3u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u gi\u00e3n n\u1edf t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi, n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn mao m\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb gi\u00e3n v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n, g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u1ed5i g\u00e2n m\u00e1u tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3767\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3767\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3767\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-3-2.webp\" alt=\"Th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-3-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-3-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-3-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-3-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"roi-loan-noi-tiet-to\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n mang thai, sau sinh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n m\u00e3n kinh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u01b0\u1edbi da gi\u00e3n n\u1edf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra do hormone estrogen t\u0103ng cao, l\u00e0m th\u00e0nh m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u y\u1ebfu \u0111i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tac-dong-tu-ton-thuong-tren-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft b\u1ea7m t\u00edm, tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc hay t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean da m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u1ee1 c\u00e1c mao m\u1ea1ch nh\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu da b\u1ea1n v\u1ed1n m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu, c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u01b0\u1edbi da s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 ra, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 g\u00f2 m\u00e1 hay m\u0169i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-mong-lo-mao-mach-tai-nha-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u01b0\u1edbi da. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o ngay nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3768\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3768\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3768\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-4-2.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-4-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-4-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-4-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-4-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3768\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-lam-diu-giam-viem\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c <\/span><b>da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da. T\u00ecm c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">rau m\u00e1, cam th\u1ea3o, tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i&#8230;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201cc\u1ee9u tinh\u201d cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1eb7t m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch th\u00eam tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-do-am-cho-lan-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch. Khi da \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u l\u1ed9 r\u00f5.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3769\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3769\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3769\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2.webp\" alt=\"Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3769\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e3y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da nh\u01b0 Vitamin K, peptides, tranexamic Acid, EGF, FGF, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1, hoa c\u00fac tr\u1eafng&#8230;. N\u1ebfu da \u0111ang qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c lotion m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tham-khao-y-kien-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1ecfng n\u1ed5i m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y da li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u1eedng \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1ed5i g\u00e2n m\u00e1u li ti ho\u1eb7c nghi ng\u1edd m\u1eafc tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 \u0111\u1ecf, b\u00e1c s\u0129 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ed1c ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u1eebng t\u1ef1 \u00fd d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-khoi-anh-nang-mat-troi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00c1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u201ck\u1ebb th\u00f9\u201d c\u1ee7a da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch. Tia UV kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu th\u00eam t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u gi\u00e3n n\u1edf r\u00f5 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00f3n r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh, \u0111eo k\u00ednh r\u00e2m, m\u1eb7c qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o d\u00e0i tay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh ra ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o khung gi\u1edd n\u1eafng g\u1eaft t\u1eeb 10h \u2013 16h.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-retinoids-de-cung-co-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng Retinoids \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinoids kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ecfng n\u1ed5i m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Retinoids c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t, \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eb9 khi m\u1edbi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-tu-ben-trong-bang-che-do-an-uong-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch. B\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 vitamin s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3756\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Rau c\u1ee7, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y t\u01b0\u01a1i: C\u00e0 r\u1ed1t, cam, kiwi, b\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh,\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Omega-3: D\u1ea7u oliu, c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i, h\u1ea1t chia.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Protein n\u1ea1c: Th\u1ecbt g\u00e0, tr\u1ee9ng, \u0111\u1eadu l\u0103ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin E: B\u01a1, h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n, \u00f3c ch\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin A: Gan b\u00f2, khoai lang, c\u00e0 chua.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia, \u0111\u1ed3 cay n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e3n m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u, khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1eb7t m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch th\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mong-yeu-lo-mao-mach-nen-dung-gi-%e2%80%93-serum-phuc-hoi-da\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? &#8211; Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, serum l\u00e0 \u201ctr\u1ee3 th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c\u201d gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i serum ch\u1ee9a:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2490\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2490\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2490\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2490\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da GSC<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium DNA: k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa m\u00f4 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bifida Ferment Lysate (S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean men c\u1ee7a vi l\u1ee3i khu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng Bifidobacterium Longum, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i vi khu\u1ea9n axit lactic h\u1eefu \u00edch c\u00f3 trong h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi): l\u00e0m \u1ea9m, l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m da, t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa DNA, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y, t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">EGF, FGF: K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, nguy\u00ean b\u00e0o s\u1ee3i: Collagen, Elastin gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i HRBV v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn serum c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00ed da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c <\/span><b>da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c khoa h\u1ecdc, dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd s\u1edbm s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n! \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean l\u01b0u ngay website c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u tin t\u1ee9c nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Da m\u1ecfng l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u0103n kho\u0103n c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, GSC s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea5t t\u1ea7n t\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3764,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2991","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2991"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3978,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991\/revisions\/3978"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3764"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2991"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2991"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2991"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}"